data.title: King Christian IX of Denmark with his family
data.meta_description: Photograph from an album of a group portrait including King Christian IX of Denmark and some of his children and grandchildren, plus a French bulldog, probably belonging to Princess Marie dOrleans, at Smystrop.From left to right: Prince George of Greece (1869-1957), Princess Alexandra (1844-1925), later Queen Alexandra, her father Christian IX (1818-1906); Dowager Empress Maria Feodorovna (1847-1928); Tsar Nicholas II (1894-1917); King George I of Greece (1845-1913); Queen Louise of Denmark (1817...
